---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Kalyan AI | AI systems that make business easier to run and grow"
	description="We build AI systems that make your business easier to run and grow, shaped around how your business works and supported after delivery."
>
	<main class="flex flex-col gap-16">
		<section class="relative overflow-hidden px-6 py-12 md:px-10 lg:px-12">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.2] blur-3xl glow-animate bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_18%_30%,rgba(10,170,231,0.2),transparent_45%),radial-gradient(circle_at_78%_55%,rgba(171,113,247,0.18),transparent_42%)]"></div>
			<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl">
				<div class="ka-card rounded-[22px] p-6 md:p-8 shadow-[0_18px_60px_-45px_rgba(0,0,0,0.35)] backdrop-blur">
					<div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--text)] md:space-y-5">
						<p class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--primary)] bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-[var(--brand-navy)]">
							Systems, built and run with you
						</p>
						<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight text-[var(--brand-navy)] md:text-5xl">
							We build AI systems that make your business easier to run and grow.
						</h1>
						<p class="copy-narrow max-w-3xl text-sm text-[var(--muted)] md:text-xl">
							We learn how your business works, find where AI will have the biggest impact, and build the right system around it.
						</p>
						<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 md:gap-3.5">
							<a class="rounded-full bg-[var(--accent-teal)] px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-white shadow-sm transition duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-[var(--secondary)] md:px-5 md:py-3 md:text-base" href="/contact#book" data-plausible="BookACall">
								Book a conversation
							</a>
							<a href="/how-we-build/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-2 border-2 border-[var(--primary)] text-sm text-[var(--primary)] rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-[var(--primary)] hover:text-white transition-colors md:px-6 md:py-3 md:text-base">See how we build</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card text-center space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 px-4 py-8 md:px-10">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">The Kalyan AI approach</h2>
			<p class="copy-narrow text-lg text-[var(--primary)] text-center mx-auto max-w-3xl">We do not come in with a fixed product.</p>
			<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)] text-center mx-auto max-w-3xl">We look at how your business actually runs, where decisions get stuck, where growth is being held back, and where AI can support the work properly.</p>
		</section>

		<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 flex flex-col gap-6">
			<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Built around how your business actually works</h2>
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-lg text-[var(--primary)]">The system should fit the business, not force the business to fit the system.</p>
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">That means understanding the people, tools, data, handoffs, approvals, and customer moments that matter before deciding what to build.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Your business, your decisions</h2>
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-lg text-[var(--primary)]">It is your business, your decisions.</p>
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">We make sure the system behind it supports you properly, with clear ownership, sensible approvals, and people involved where judgment matters.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
				<div class="space-y-3">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">How we build and support the system</h2>
					<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-lg text-[var(--primary)]">Every serious system we deliver is planned, risk-assessed, built in controlled phases, tested, documented, and supported after go-live.</p>
					<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">That is what separates a reliable business system from a demo that only works in simple conditions.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Discover</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">We learn how the business runs, what matters most, and where the right system could help.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Scope</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">We define the outcome, risks, dependencies, success criteria, and what is deliberately out of scope.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Build</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">We deliver in controlled phases, with clear boundaries, testing, and human review at each step.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Operate</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">We host, monitor, support, and improve the system after go-live.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<a href="/how-we-build/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-[var(--primary)] text-[var(--primary)] rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-[var(--primary)] hover:text-white transition-colors">See how we build</a>
			</section>
		</div>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<div class="space-y-3">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">See what this looks like in practice</h2>
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto max-w-3xl text-[var(--primary)]">Examples of systems built around real business operations.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
				<div class="space-y-2 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-5 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Kalyan AI internal system</h3>
					<p class="text-[var(--muted)]">A working view of how enquiries, decisions, and owner review can sit in one system.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-2 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-5 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Spa by Kaajal</h3>
					<p class="text-[var(--muted)]">Finance admin reduced from around 4 hours weekly to around 30 minutes.</p>
					<a href="/case-studies" class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)] hover:text-[var(--secondary)]">Read the case study</a>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-2 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-5 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Client booking and operations</h3>
					<p class="text-[var(--muted)]">A client booking and operations system we recently built and tested.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Built for trust</h2>
			<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
				<div class="space-y-1 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
					<p class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Clear ownership and approvals</p>
					<p class="text-[var(--muted)]"><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Every decision has an owner</span>, approvals are explicit, and nothing moves without a named accountable person.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-1 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
					<p class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Guardrails and auditability</p>
					<p class="text-[var(--muted)]"><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Controls, logs, and checkpoints</span> are built in so you can see what happened and why.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-1 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
					<p class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Evidence and reporting</p>
					<p class="text-[var(--muted)]"><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Signals and actions</span> are summarised into concise reports that leaders can review quickly.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-1 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
					<p class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Monitoring and support</p>
					<p class="text-[var(--muted)]"><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">We host and monitor</span> the system, handle issues, and keep it aligned with your operating reality.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-1 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
					<p class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Training and handover</p>
					<p class="text-[var(--muted)]"><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">We train your team</span> and leave clear documentation so the system sticks.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
